    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is acknowledged; the shortfall is mitigated by the strong quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96) and the limited clinical consequence of the single-condition gap. Re-validation under additional loading configurations is planned for the next model revision cycle. The material property dataset (vintage 2025-Q3) and bench test dataset (vintage 2025-Q4) predate the current model revision date (2026-02-14); formal re-validation against the updated model build is planned but not yet executed.",
